g.text: <left>: The left-hand side of an equation. See
an extension point for stripe skipping as well as specializations of the left-hand side
<right>: The right-hand side of an equation. See
an extension point for stripe skipping as well as specializations of the right-hand side
Equations contain a pair of terms, a left-hand side and a right-hand side.
equations have orientation as an attribute with default
